frames.caption: A towering anthropomorphic wolf with muscular build stands confidently amidst a crowd in a rugged, ancient setting. The creature is adorned with a leather strap and a cloth wrap, exuding a sense of power and authority. Onlookers appear captivated and perhaps wary, as they observe the imposing figure.
